{"tid":776314,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"法國連登真係創意沙漠黎","createTime":"2018-08-12T03:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T14:49:50.000Z","uid":68867,"like":5,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bc21eba297020378f398f75461694f5c5f20cdbc","tid":776314,"uid":68867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:03:04.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 開左個搞笑創意post俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住俾大家笑下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩女朋友幫我含完 之後...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/775798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/775798</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 個撚個撚係到屌屌屌屌屌屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬哩到創意台啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又唔係po係時事台阻撚住人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我知道都有好多人都覺得好好笑 同 笑到碌曬地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好多謝你地ge支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要係我個post夠撚曬創新<br />\n哩類topic係連登 丁丁擔保唔過10個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以話連登真係兒登黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5442b305afb14b0c5a5d2c3c829c1ddb593cf9","tid":776314,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T03:03:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">岩牙</span>"},{"pid":"211977f7856f60435ab4acb2287d80ba65569c68","tid":7